org.apache.paimon.flink.source

Class DataTableSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.paimon.flink.source.FlinkTableSource
      • org.apache.paimon.flink.source.DataTableSource

  • public class DataTableSource
extends FlinkTableSource
    Table source to create StaticFileStoreSource or ContinuousFileStoreSource under batch mode or change-tracking is disabled. For streaming mode with change-tracking enabled and FULL scan mode, it will create a HybridSource of LogHybridSourceFactory.FlinkHybridFirstSource and kafka log source created by LogSourceProvider.
